      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i was out for a run in stanley park and i tripped really hard on some tree roots. my ankle is super swollen now and it hurts a lot. i cant really walk on it or put any weight on it without it feeling like it's gonna snap lol. u think i just need to do some ice and rest for a bit? like the RICE thing?",
