    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks, that sounds more manageable. i already have some ibuprofen here. is it safe if i take like 800mg every few hours if the pain is really bad? i just want to get the swelling down as fast as possible so i can get back to running. also, would it be okay to try and walk on it a bit tomorrow if the ibuprofen kicks in?",
